text: The fifth season of Hawaii Five-O premiered on September 12, 1972 and ended March 13, 1973. 24 episodes aired during this season. The Region 1 DVD was released on November 18, 2008. == Episodes == ==Categories== Category:1972 American television seasons Category:1973 American television seasons 05
